Use the formulas below to calculate \(\hat{\beta}_1\), the estimated slope, and \(\hat{\beta}_0\), the estimated intercept.
\[
\begin{aligned}
&\hat{\beta}_1 = r \frac{s_y}{s_x} \\
&\hat{\beta}_0 = \bar{y} - \hat{\beta}_1 \bar{x}
\end{aligned}
\]

